{"about_the_game":"Minecart Madness is a 2D arcade infinite-runner in the style of early platforming games. Take on the role of an ape in a minecart and ride the rails as far as you can while dodging inbound minecarts and leaping over gaps in the track.<br><br>The game features a variety of game modes, each introducing new challenges and gameplay opportunities:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Classic - standard, balanced gameplay<br></li><li> Superflat - like classic, but all track segments generate at the same vertical height<br></li><li> Low gravity - enables longer air time at the expense of jump accuracy<br></li><li> Too much brake - near-limitless braking ability<br></li><li> Ultra mega - enemy carts spawn more frequently and move faster<br></li><li> Late start - start with more points and gain an initial speed-boost<br></li><li> Crocodile craze - holes don't spawn, and enemies spawn more frequently<br></li><li> No holes barred - enemies don't spawn, and holes spawn more frequently</li></ul><br>All game modes can also be played with two players on the same system in split-screen multiplayer.<br><br>Minecart Madness supports keyboard and controller input modes for one or two players. All inputs are customizable.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Why do you look familiar...?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876750/f6c9f5ac91001f51749c167dec040529135ce890.jpg"},{"name":"Crocodile Oddity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876750/b813a650a2c517c8eca0272732eb9723d69642ef.jpg"},{"name":"Crocodile Craze","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876750/f385a9750a2a6d87222303d5d653e6a630800d68.jpg"},{"name":"Crocodile Insanity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1876750/db2e1b75aa6f88e68675bc062330ea4c23cdd423.jpg"},{"name":"Crocodile Madness","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommuni